Package org.uclab.mm.kcl.edkat.service

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ConclusionService
    This is service interface for the Conclusion it provides interfaces to create, update, retrieve of Conclusion of a specific rule
    ConditionService
    This is service interface for the Condition it provides interfaces to create, update, retrieve of condition of a specific rule
    RuleService
    This is service interface class for the rule it provides interfaces to create, update, retrieve of rules, conditions, conclusions, and situation
    SituationService
    This is service interface for the situation this service interface provides create, update, retrieve of situations of some specific rule
    UserService
    This is service interface for the user it provides service interface to create, update, retrieve of user
    WellnessConceptsModelService
    This is service interface for the wellness model, it provides service interfaces to create, update, retrieve of wellness concepts
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConclusionServiceImpl
    This is service implementation for the Conclusion it provides implementation to create, update, retrieve of Conclusion of a specific rule
    ConditionServiceImpl
    This is service implementation for the Condition it provides implementation to create, update, retrieve of condition of a specific rule
    RuleServiceImpl
    This is service implementation class for the rule it provides implementation to create, update, retrieve of rules, conditions, conclusions, and situation
    SituationServiceImpl
    This is implementation for the situation this implemenation class provides create, update, retrieve of situations of some specific rule
    UserServiceImpl
    This is service implementation for the user it provides service implementation to create, update, retrieve of user
    WellnessConceptsModelServiceImpl
    This is service implementation for the wellness model, it provides service implementation to create, update, retrieve of wellness concepts
